Titolo: This Land Is My Land

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: This Land is My Land is a stealth action video game developed and published by Game Labs. It was released in early access for Microsoft Windows in 2019, prior to its full release in October 2021. The game is set in the 19th-century American frontier and features a Native American protagonist resisting the white settlers. It has been criticised for perpetuating stereotypes and for having no indigenous people involved in its development.

